103
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:55,580
[SPEAKER_00] Tri?

104
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,580
[SPEAKER_00] Da, tri.

105
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:57,580
[SPEAKER_00] Rećiš mi koja treća.

106
00:12:57,580 --> 00:13:00,580
[SPEAKER_00] Behavioralni marketing je nekako zapravo...

107
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:01,580
[SPEAKER_00] Neuro i šoper.

108
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:02,580
[SPEAKER_00] Neuro i šoper.

109
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,580
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

110
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:14,580
[SPEAKER_00] Neuro, zapravo ti do podataka koje koristite za potrebe klijenata, dolaziš snimajući mozak, jel tako?

111
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:16,580
[SPEAKER_00] Da, između...

112
00:13:16,580 --> 00:13:22,580
[SPEAKER_00] Tok je mozak, recimo, pod nekakvom impresijom nekakvih oglasa ili što god.

113
00:13:22,580 --> 00:13:24,580
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo kojih stimulusa, da.

114
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:25,580
[SPEAKER_00] Stimulusa, jel.

115
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:30,580
[SPEAKER_00] Znači tu govorimo o hardware, ili tako? Snimate hardware i gledamo šta se događa.

116
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:42,580
[SPEAKER_00] S druge strane, behavioralni marketing ili ta znanost zapravo više promatra tu osobu kao psihološki, ili tako?

117
00:13:42,580 --> 00:13:45,580
[SPEAKER_00] Kao kroz nekakav software. Šta sam ti htio podijeliti?

118
00:13:45,580 --> 00:13:48,580
